venue.name: Toby Keith's I Love This Bar & Grill

item.description:
Hello ladies!

Happy Halloween to all and hopefully everyone is recovering from the "Nor'Easter" we had this past weekend:-)

 "A Country Mile" is playing at Toby Keith's Friday 12/2 and they sound like a great cover band.  I checked out the reviews and I guess they tend to cover Lady Antebellum, Sugarland, Jason Aldeen etc etc.  They go on at 9.30pm and I imagine that the bar will get packed.  There aren't many tables so I won't be making reservations but would still appreciate an accurate count of those who plan to attend.

Look forward to seeing old and new faces!!

 

Lisa
item.how_to_find_us: As the date nears I will send out an email about exact time/location to congregate when we get to the venue
